Review Text: I ordered 2 shawarmas, one was averaged sized. The other was a miniature. There is inconsistency in size, the taste is not worthy of a praise. The some chunks of chicken felt raw while chewing, they were delivered cold. Please save your money and time, there are definitely significantly better places to eat shawarmas from.

Not knowing about the shawarma spots in the locality of gachibowli. Out of cravings, ordered rumali special shawarma and surprisingly the shawarma was #fabulous, although the ratings were average. The food amazed me completely. The chicken was very juicy also crisp (a different kind of shawarma). The amount of chicken loaded inside was really good. I suggest to go or order from this place and have a taste of it.
